  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Climate change is a major threat to producers in Eastern Africa, with increasing temperatures and changes in disease patterns. This is evident with a number of Fairtrade producers. TWIN Trading works to help producers take practical steps to overcome the challenges of climate change, to better understand the issues and to take steps to deal with its consequences. This may include crop diversification and influencing government agricultural extension programmes to be more aware of climate change. As a result of this project, Fairtrade producers have a better understanding of climate change and the attendant risks, and have developed practical plans to cope with the changes</narrative>
  </description>
